      informatics. As a community, we aim to empower and encourage all women++ bioinformaticians through regular
      meetings, networking events and workshops. We seek to give a platform to women++ professionals, including those
      members of other underrepresented groups in science, such as BIPOC, the LGBTQIA+ community, and people with
      disabilities.
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="image">
      <center>
        <Image
          src={'/photos/meetup_20240918.jpg'}
          width="750"
          height="537"
          decoding="async"
          loading="lazy"
